(33, 'Vision and Mission', '<p><span style="font-size:16px"><em><strong>Vision</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Realization of educational units faithful, devoted to the graduates who excelled in achievement, national character and care for the environment and be able to compete in the global era</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Mision</strong></span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Organize teaching and learning activities are effective and efficient (adequate learning resources)</li>\r\n	<li>Organizing cooperation with universities and other institutions.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizing academic activities and nonacademic as a place for students to develop their potential optimally.</li>\r\n	<li>Implement school rules consistently.</li>\r\n	<li>Promote the spirit of religious life and realize inter-religious harmony.</li>\r\n	<li>Perform extracurricular activities at regular intervals that can foster a sense of social responsibility to learners.</li>\r\n	<li>Creating a school culture that loves the environment.</li>\r\n	<li>Involve parents / guardians of students to provide guidance on good manners.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordination and communication with parents, the community, government and private institutions.</li>\r\n	<li>Implement the development program self-learners to recognize their potential so as to develop it.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 7, '2015-08-12 11:13:39', 1, 1, 1),
(34, 'History', '<p style="text-align:justify">Established since 1983, SMAN 2 Salatiga located on Tegalrejo Raya 79 St, District Argomulyo, Salatiga, occupies a land area of ??28,950 m2. At the beginning of its development, namely in 1984 (previously occupied the building SMA 1 Salatiga) this region is still quiet because not many houses. After occupying the new school building itself although three classes, SMANDA (call for SMAN 2 Salatiga) continued to experience good growth on the number of students, teachers and achievements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Imposed curriculum had been developed starting from the curriculum in 1975, followed the new curriculum in 1994 and developed into the Competency Based Curriculum (CBC) in 2004, Education Unit Level Curriculum (SBC) and refined into 2013 that the current curriculum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Powered by educators and education personnel are competent and dedicated SMAN 2 Salatiga managed to achieve many good achievements of students, teachers and the school itself. Good cooperation with various print and electronic media as well as WEB that can be visited by the public to make SMAN 2 Salatiga many widely known in Salatiga.</p>\r\n', 7, '2015-08-12 11:35:44', 1, 1, 1),
(35, 'Goals', '<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Short-term Goals:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>The average value rose 0.5 National Examination of 2015</li>\r\n	<li>Eighty-five percent of the students have a sense of discipline, piety and social care is high enough, so that it becomes assets that support the achievement of the school.</li>\r\n	<li>Students who go on to college rose 15% from 2015</li>\r\n	<li>Education-oriented life skills (life skills) are implemented through extracurricular activities</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize the use and provision of sufficient resources gradually Improve relations and cooperation with related institutions / organizations.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain &quot;A&quot; of accredited schools</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Medium-term Goals.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Improvement of qualification of teachers (25% S2)</li>\r\n	<li>Upgrading the qualifications of Education (minimum D3)</li>\r\n	<li>All teachers mastering ICT</li>\r\n	<li>Increasing the number of students who enter high diperguruan (minimum 50%)</li>\r\n	<li>Science Olympiad team has a top-3 city level.</li>\r\n	<li>Having a team sport and art who won city and provincial level.</li>\r\n	<li>Adding the IPS laboratory facilities, Multimedia and Language</li>\r\n	<li>The addition of the learning space to support the learning process</li>\r\n	<li>Procurement 1 representative student council room.</li>\r\n	<li>Procurement Guidance Room, Teacher Room and&nbsp; Master Headmaster standard Room.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Long-Term Goals</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Increased school status (to the top schools)</li>\r\n	<li>Improving the ability of teachers in the English language from passive to active.</li>\r\n	<li>All qualified educators minimal S2</li>\r\n	<li>Having a football field representative.</li>\r\n	<li>Has a tennis court field representative.</li>\r\n	<li>Having a science olympiad team that won the national level.</li>\r\n	<li>Has audio-visual room and a recording studio.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 7, '2015-08-12 11:35:09', 1, 1, 1),
